title: Food Network's 'Pioneer Woman' Talks Motherhood + Little Debbie Cake Rankings + Brantley Gilbert On Being Home With The Kids
itunes:title: Food Network's 'Pioneer Woman' Talks Motherhood + Little Debbie Cake Rankings + Brantley Gilbert On Being Home With The Kids
description:
Food Network's Ree Drummond, known as 'Pioneer Woman' joins the show. Bobby's girlfriend Caitlyn asks her questions about motherhood and even asks for some cooking tips so she can impress Bobby in the kitchen. Bobby and Amy rate their favorite Little Debbie snacks. Plus, Brantley Gilbert joins the show and shares how the quarantine life is giving him more time to watch his kids grow up!
